{
  "id": "adv_event_2211_01_05",
  "title": "喧嘩するほど\n仲がいい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――そして、翌朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――and the next morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それで全員……いや芽衣以外、酔っ払ったまま\nまとめてこの部屋で寝落ちしてしまったと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So everyone …… except for Mei‚ who fell asleep\nin this room together while drunk. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2,
      "endTime": 10.1423807143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "……面目次第もございません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am deeply ashamed of myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3333333333,
      "endTime": 13.2038775762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "うう、頭がガンガンする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ my head is pounding……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4,
      "endTime": 18.4067799568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、kanaは酔っ払ってないからね\nめんどくさくなって、そのままここで寝ただけだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "wait‚ kana is not drunk.\nI just fell asleep here because it became\ntoo much of a hassle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6,
      "endTime": 26.5116552353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も！\nみんなでお喋りして一緒に寝るの、楽しかったよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei too!\nIt was fun chatting with everyone and sleeping together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7,
      "endTime": 31.8488435744,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_futon-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5566.666666699998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、よく寝た……\n……って今、何時！？　今日はライブ本番なのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaaa‚ I slept well ……\nWhat time is ……?　I'm supposed to be at the live today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4,
      "endTime": 38.966371726999995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "今すぐ出る準備しないと……\n…………あら？　貴方達、何してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to get ready to leave now……\n………… Eh? What are you girls doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1666666667,
      "endTime": 45.88619038269999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、昨日の夜のこと覚えてない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… don't you remember last night by any chance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1,
      "endTime": 51.0748752594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "昨日？　確か、ロビーでろくでもない話になって……\nそういえば、なんで貴方達と同じ部屋にいるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yesterday? I think we were in the lobby\ntalking about some shit. ……\nCome to think of it‚ why am I in the same room with yours?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2666666667,
      "endTime": 61.010385576800005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "マジか、酒飲んだ後のこと全部忘れてるとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously‚ you've forgotten everything after a few drinks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2,
      "endTime": 66.50086164470001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "三人とも、のんびりしてる場合じゃないんですよ！\n九時には会場入りです、急いで支度して下さい！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is not the time for all three of you to be relaxing!\nWe'll be at the venue at 9 o'clock‚\nso hurry up and get ready!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7,
      "endTime": 73.38217687609999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ sir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5666666667,
      "endTime": 75.1227890889,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1666.6666665999942
