    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "行ってらっしゃ～い\nスリクスさん達、今日のライブも頑張ってね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have a great day!\nGood luck at today's live‚ ⅢX!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3,
      "endTime": 83.2033558846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……せっかく温泉に連れて来てもらったけど\nリフレッシュどころか、余計に疲れた気がするわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa…… I've been taken to a hot spring‚\nbut instead of feeling refreshed‚\nI'm feeling even more tired. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6333333333,
      "endTime": 91.7154421171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、幽霊の出る旅館とは思わなかったし\nスリクスさんの喧嘩にはずっと付き合わされるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't expect a ryokan to be haunted‚\nand I've had to deal with ⅢX's bickering for a long time. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9,
      "endTime": 99.34811801910001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あはは。でも芽衣は楽しかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha. But Mei had fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.5333333333,
      "endTime": 103.28648527460001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "……三人集まれば、喧嘩しかしない人達だけど\nでも、あれはあれで仲がいいんだとよく分かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… when the three of us get together‚ all we do is fight.\nBut I could tell that they got along well with that one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5,
      "endTime": 111.006530571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと喧嘩してるのに仲がいい？　どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They fight all the time‚ but they get along? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2,
      "endTime": 115.99990940090001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "そのくらいの距離が楽なのよ、きっと\n……ほら、私はみんなより少し大人だから分かるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's easy to be that close‚ I guess.\n…… See‚ I'm a little more mature than\neveryone else‚ so I get it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2,
      "endTime": 124.0093421937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2211_01_05-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "良く分かんないけど……大人って、大変なんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know‚ but …… it's hard being an adult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.2,
      "endTime": 129.9120407104,
      "sfxList": []
